{{Top|leg}}
An '''accelerator gate''' was one component of the type of projectile cannon that was primarily found within the garbage launchers on the [[Ecumenopolis/Legends|ecumenopolis]] of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. It was through these gates that all of the non-recyclable garbage that the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] generated, stuffed into massive sealed capsules, was shot out of the gravity well and typically sent either into orbit or to impact on one of the capital world's four [[Moon/Legends|moons]]. Squatters sometimes blocked accelerator gates with their impromptu housing; one such incident caused a misfire, which killed everyone living inside the gate and several others around the area.

